06445658,-0.02642271,0.04333853,-0.01078224,-0.02253043,0.07001544,0.22949718,0.04136701,0.02888373,-0.00726451,0.01072311,0.00766069,0.07426471,0.03661551,-0.01070236,-0.00368821,0.10539824,-0.00590726,0.03170629,0.04837119,-0.03270459,0.043674,0.03839888,-0.01072019,0.03578658,-0.01634527,-0.0801387,0.02174806,0.08791001,0.05038953,0.00129012,-0.07523731,0.00331875,0.04618124,-0.0486607,0.01271567,0.01911527,-0.00078175,0.00025949,0.04812277,0.00583266,-0.02155968,-0.00873059,-0.01201396,0.02957578,0.00462026,0.01739966,0.10951302,0.04668182],"last_embed":{"hash":"1ofvx6s","tokens":399}}},"last_read":{"hash":"1ofvx6s","at":1769676350640},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1729267034000,"size":11575,"at":1769676327038,"hash":"1ofvx6s"},"blocks":{"#":[1,241],"##{1}":[1,22],"##{2}":[23,27],"##{3}":[28,33],"##{4}":[34,34],"##{5}":[35,35],"##{6}":[36,36],"##{7}":[44,44],"##{8}":[45,45],"##{9}":[46,50],"##{10}":[51,51],"##{11}":[52,58],"##{12}":[59,71],"##{13}":[72,80],"##{14}":[81,85],"##{15}":[86,218],"##{16}":[219,241]},"outlinks":[{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":36},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":44},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":52},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":59},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":72},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":81},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":87},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":123},{"title":"1,2)$\n        - (3) $\\left(-\\frac{6}{7}, 4\\right)$\n    - 解析\n        - (1) 已知 $p(x)=|x-3|, q(x)=4-|x-5|$\n        - \n        - 由 $p(x)<q(x)$ ，即 $|x-3|+|x-5|<4$\n        - 当 $x \\geq 5$ 时, 不等式化为 $x-3+x-5<4$, 得 $x<6$,\n        - 此时，不等式的解为 $5 \\leq x<6$ 。\n        - 当 $3 \\leq x<5$ 时, 不等式化为 $x-3+5-x<4$, 即 $2<4$, 恒成立,\n        - 此时，不等式的解为 $3 \\leq x<5$ 。\n        - 当 $x<3$ 时, 不等式化为 $3-x+5-x<4$, 得 $x>2$.\n        - 此时，不等式的解为 $2<x<3$ 。\n        - 综上所述, $p(x)<q(x)$ 的解集为 $(2,6)$, 即 $T(p(x), q(x))=(2,6)$.\n        - (2) 由题意知, 不等式 $x-1<(x-a)^{2}+2 a$ (1)恒成立,\n        - \n        - 且不等式 $(x-a)^{2}+2 a<a(x-1)^{2}+62$ 2恒成立;\n        - 由(1) 得， $x^{2}-(2 a+1) x+\\left(a^{2}+2 a+1\\right)>0$ ，\n        - 则 $\\Delta=(2 a+1)^{2}-4\\left(a^{2}+2 a+1\\right)<0$, 解得 $a>-\\frac{3}{4}$;\n        - 由 $(2)$ 得， $(a-1) x^{2}-a^{2}-a+6>0$ ，\n        - 当 $a=1$ 时，不等式化为 $-1-1+6>0$ 恒成立，\n        - 当 $a \\neq 1$ 时, 应满足 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}a-1>0 \\\\ -a^{2}-a+6>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 解得 $1<a<2$;\n        - 综上知, $a$ 的取值范围是 $[1,2)$.\n        - (3) 已知 $f(x)=|2 x-b|, g(x)=\\frac{x+4 b}{x-1}, h(x)=2$,\n        - \n        - 由题意得, 不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解,\n        - 由 $f(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow-2<2 x-b<2 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{b}{2}-1<x<\\frac{b}{2}+1$,\n        - 又 $g(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x+4 b}{x-1}<2 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x+4 b-2(x-1)}{x-1}<0 \\Leftrightarrow \\frac{x-(4 b+2)}{x-1}>0$,\n        - (1)当 $4 b+2=1$, 即 $b=-\\frac{1}{4}$ 时, 上式为 $1>0$, 对任意 $x \\in(-\\infty, 1) \\cup(1,+\\infty)$ 恒成立.此时不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解，满足题意；\n        - (2) 当 $4 b+2<1$, 即 $b<-\\frac{1}{4}$ 时, $g(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow x<4 b+2$ 或 $x>1$,\n        - \n        - 要使不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解, 则 $\\frac{b}{2}-1<4 b+2$ 或 $\\frac{b}{2}+1>1$, 解得 $b>-\\frac{6}{7}$,\n        - 则有 $-\\frac{6}{7}<b<-\\frac{1}{4}$;\n        - (3) 当 $4 b+2>1$, 即 $b>-\\frac{1}{4}$ 时, $g(x)<2 \\Leftrightarrow x<1$ 或 $x>4 b+2$.\n        - \n        - 要使不等式组 $\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}f(x)<2 \\\\ g(x)<2\\end{array}\\right.$ 有解,\n        - 则 $\\frac{b}{2}-1<1$ 或 $\\frac{b}{2}+1>4 b+2$, 解得 $b<4$,\n        - 则有 $-\\frac{1}{4}<b<4$ ；\n        - 综上所述, $b$ 的取值范围是 $\\left(-\\frac{6}{7}, 4\\right)$.\n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- \n- ### 集合类似的题目\n    - > [🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":175},{"title":"🔖","target":"🔖.md","line":234}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[],"last_embed":{"hash":"1ofvx6s","at":1769676350432}},"smart_blocks:RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/打印.md#": {"path